<h2>Business Administration</h2>

<p> 
 This degree provides students with a foundational understanding of the functional areas in business. 
 Students must select one of the following majors to complete the B.S.B.A. degree:
 (1) Finance with concentrations in Finance, Finance/Accounting, or Risk Management and Insurance; 
 (2) International Business;
 (3) Management; (4) Management Information Systems, (5) Marketing, and (6) Operations and Supply Chain Management.
</p>

